  "keyFeatures": [
    "High-performance HTTP/1.1 client with connection pooling and pipelining",
    "WHATWG-compliant fetch() implementation powering Node.js built-in fetch",
    "Flexible dispatcher architecture (Client, Pool, Agent, ProxyAgent)",
    "Built-in interceptors for caching, retries, redirects, and DNS",
    "Comprehensive mocking support via MockAgent, MockClient, and SnapshotAgent",
    "WebSocket and EventSource (SSE) client support",
    "HTTP/2 Cleartext (H2C) support",
    "SOCKS5 proxy support via Socks5ProxyAgent",
    "Cookie and MIME type utilities",
    "Diagnostics channel integration for observability"
  ],
